Title: <tt>mongodb_instance</tt>: Go CRIT is instance is down
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1615375650
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

The check plugin <tt>mongodb_instance</tt>, which monitors the current
instance of the MongoDB, will now go CRIT if the instance is down. Before,
the plugin reported this in its output, but this was not reflected by the
monitoring status.
